devdoc.details: This contract's allows decentralized execution of on-chain recurring tasks. It requires three main components:     1. A source for creating transactions requests     2. A transaction delegate with the recurring transaction scheduled     3. A funded delegated wallet with the transaction delegate set as a delegate
